This repository — "AI Archives Workspace — HDH 7200 Digital Archiving Systems" —
is the educational material of the course HDH 7200 (Digital Archiving Systems)
taught by Prof. Hyeji Jung at the Royal Institute of Traditional Arts ×
Korea National University of Cultural Heritage, Masters in Digital Heritage (MDH),
Year 1, Semester 2, 2026.

